movies.title: The Constant Factor
movies.summary: A young man is facing death of his mother. A petty corruption at his job leads to him being framed and robbed of his only desire to climb mountains in Himalayas, as his father did and where he died.

movies.title: Same Time, Next Christmas
movies.summary: Olivia and Jeff met at Hawaii every Christmas growing up. In their teens their friendship was on the verge of developing into something else when Jeff's mother died and his family stopped coming. Olivia's family has kept the Christmas-in-Hawaii tradition going, though. One Christmas Olivia, now a up-and-coming architect, suddenly meets Jeff again. He, his sister, and their dad have decided to revive the tradition. Jeff is processing a divorce and they find that the spark is still there but circumstances pull them apart again. What will next Christmas bring?
